reviewText: Didn't care much for the movie.

Richard Pryor he's not... well, actually, I can't say that, because I didn't know Richard in his personal life. But Harry Lennix is a good actor (go watch Dollhouse if you don't believe me). I did buy this movie because my friend was supposed to be in it - he's listed in the credits - but I guess he wound up on the cutting room floor.
